  ('ENG.6.8.001', 'İngilizce', 6, 8, 'Ünite 8', 'L1. Students can get ready for the listening/watching-comprehension process for the current content on “life in the universe and future with planets and the Earth as a planet; life on Earth in the future” carefully.', 'a) Students activate their pre-existing knowledge and experience related to the current theme and content by recalling their background knowledge imaginatively in her/his own language without speaking it. b) Students identify significant relationships between their pre-existing knowledge and experiences and the clues to the current content without translation. c) Students make predictions about the current content on “life in the universe and future” by using the relationships that they recognis'),
