  ('ENG.7.1.021', 'İngilizce', 7, 1, 'Ünite 1', 'S5. Students can reconstruct the information about “school life and education with extra-curricular activities at school; competitions and celebrations at school; national days and celebrations” when communicating with others.', 'a) Students use the same or similar information presented in the current content in verbal or written forms in different contexts by reorganising it meaningfully, accurately, effectively, efficiently, functionally, and individually as required. b) Students engage in verbal and/or written communication by sharing the reconstructed meaningful information about the current content with others.'),
